Features:
- everything is mobile responsive
- smooth transition to "Learn More" overlay when hovering a card's image
- slide-in and slide-out animations for modal + smooth background transition
- modal can be closed by pressing 'X' or anywhere outside of it
- until an image is completely loaded, render the loading gif
- "Learn More" and the card's title are underlined when hovered to show they
are clickable
- redux store simulates communication with a server + provides global state
